		<p class="disclaimer">This website is for informational purposes only and does not constitute legal advice.</p>
	</div>
</footer>
<style>
	footer {
		padding: 2.5em 1em;
		background: #1a2744;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		text-align: center;
	}
	.footer-content {
		max-width: 960px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.copyright {
		margin-bottom: 0.5em;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #ffffff;
	}
	.disclaimer {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
		margin: 0;
	}
</style>
